    "en": {
      "title": "No buses from Tuesday if no annual bus fare revision considered tomorrow: Gemunu",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Lanka Private Bus Owners' Association (LPBOA) today requested to consider the annual bus fare revision by tomorrow with the recent hike in the price of diesel, if no favourable response received, bus services will grind to a halt from Tuesday (28).",
        "LPBOA Chairman Gemunu Wijerathne said the annual bus fare revision comes to force\u00a0 from every July 1.",
        "\"We had to face fuel price increase in twice within a short period of time. Now, we are pushed to a situation to wind up operating buses,\" he said.",
        "Therefore, we have decided to terminate operating bus service from Tuesday (28), if we do not receive the green light to annual bus fare revision by Monday (27), Wijerathne added.(Cathuranga Samarawickrema)"
      ],
